It's just about as funny as Season 1, sometimes better, sometimes... more unique.

Guest stars this season include:
Bob Odenkirk, Zach Galifianakis, Patton Oswalt, David Cross, Rainn Wilson, John C. Reilly, Jeff Goldblum, A.D. Miles, Dave Navarro, Tom Skerritt, Maria Bamford, Will Forte, Fred Armisen, Michael Q. Schmidt and "Weird Al" Yankovic.

*This was a collection of a bunch of torrents of single episodes that I found on this site, as well as others. Yes, I messed around with the names of the files, but I left credit where credit was left by the other uploaders in order to include the episode name in the file names.*

[In your torrent viewer, S2E01 "Vacation", may appear to be last when sorted by name, this is because I forgot to UPPERCASE the "And" in the file title, the episode is still there, do not worry.]
